(1388, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2014/12/dinah/''>WordPress 4.1 “Dinah”</a> <span class="rss-date">18 diciembre, 2014</span><div class="rssSummary">Version 4.1 of WordPress, named “Dinah” in honor of jazz singer Dinah Washington, is available for download or update in your WordPress dashboard. New features in WordPress 4.1 help you focus on your writing, and the new default theme lets you show it off in style. Introducing Twenty Fifteen Our newest default theme, Twenty Fifteen, is [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://poststatus.com/new-look-new-domain/''>Post Status: A new look and a new domain</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://poststatus.com/pagely-growth-wordpress-hosting/''>Post Status: 5 years into business, Pagely is growing faster than ever</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://poststatus.com/elto-shutting-down-temporarily/''>Post Status: Website micro services provider, Elto, is shutting down for now</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Plugin popular:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Jetpack by WordPress.com</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=jetpack&amp;_wpnonce=0349787724&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Jetpack by WordPress.com''>Instalar</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
